# This directory holds model training outputs
# Created by running: python train.py
#
# Expected outputs:
# - cassava_model.keras        (trained weights)
# - class_indices.json         (class name mapping)
# - phase1_history.png         (phase 1 training curves)
# - phase2_history.png         (phase 2 training curves)
# - confusion_matrix.png       (test set confusion matrix)
